{"acceptance_criteria":"","actor":"","agent_state":"","assignee":"twosatsmaxi","await_id":"","await_type":"","close_reason":"Implemented and verified endpoint logic","closed_at":"2026-03-11T06:03:25Z","closed_by_session":"","compacted_at":null,"compacted_at_commit":null,"compaction_level":0,"content_hash":"b5d569d31ed95b1c93f0ec4f0f066e9df75cdb414419fe9ba0cfce8634b510e4","created_at":"2026-03-11T05:52:28Z","created_by":"twosatsmaxi","crystallizes":0,"defer_until":null,"description":"Add a new Axum route that returns paginated block heights for a given filter category. Used by the frontend explore page to support collection-based filtering with prev/next navigation.\n\n## Endpoint\nGET /explore/blocks?filter=\u003ccategory\u003e\u0026page=0\u0026limit=9\n\n## Query params\n- filter: string (required) — one of: punks, palindrome, sub-100k, nakamoto, patoshi, billionaire, epic-sat, pizza, pristine-punk, perfect-punk\n- page: u64 (default 0)\n- limit: u64 (default 9, max 50)\n\n## Response JSON\n{\n  heights: [u64],      // block heights for this page\n  has_more: bool,\n  has_prev: bool,      // page \u003e 0\n  total: Option\u003cu64\u003e   // if deterministic/known count\n}\n\n## Filter logic\n\n### Deterministic (pure computation, no DB needed)\n- punks: heights where height % 4 == 3\n- palindrome: heights whose decimal string is a palindrome\n- sub-100k: heights 0..99_999\n- nakamoto: heights 0..36_288 (approximate Satoshi-era)\n\n### Curated (return hardcoded representative list for now, wire real data later)\n- patoshi, billionaire, epic-sat, pizza, pristine-punk, perfect-punk: return stub data / curated arrays\n\n## Files to create/modify\n- src/routes/explore.rs (new) — handler + filter logic\n- src/routes/mod.rs — register /explore/blocks route","design":"","due_at":null,"ephemeral":0,"estimated_minutes":null,"event_kind":"","external_ref":null,"hook_bead":"","id":"bitmap-marketplace-vs2","is_template":0,"issue_type":"feature","last_activity":null,"metadata":